**Done.** Created `docs/design/automation-vocabulary-collection.md` (15KB) covering 6 automation areas:

1. **Auto-enrich on word selection** — enrichment fires in background when user selects 1-2 words; one-click "Save" button inline; optional auto-save
2. **Background enrichment queue** — new `background/enrichmentQueue.ts` with IndexedDB persistence, 3-concurrent processing, retry logic
3. **Passive vocabulary scanner** — new `content-script/vocabScanner.ts` that detects IELTS-level words on page load using tiered frequency lists, shows mini-tooltips
4. **Batch enrichment for imported content** — auto-extracts vocabulary from saved articles/videos/public API imports
5. **One-click save everywhere** — selection panel save action, right-click context menu, simplified popup forms with background enrichment
6. **Automatic topic detection** — infers topic from paragraph context, URL patterns, domain mapping

Backend changes span 16+ files across `packages/ai`, `apps/extension`, and `apps/web`. Validation: file exists.
